/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514978</guid></item><item><title>25 Martha 2025的Anecdot＃6</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514979</link><description>“分娩后有一项大运动吗？”&lt;br /&gt;我会以不同的方式提出这个问题：“大运动之后是否有分娩？”</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514979</guid></item><item><title>25 Martha 2025的轶事＃7</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514980</link><description>有两个醉汉：&lt;br /&gt; - 你为什么这么红？&lt;br /&gt; - 是的，我现在是领导者！&lt;br /&gt; - 什么领导者？&lt;br /&gt; - 红色 - 鲁布！</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514980</guid></item><item><title>25 Martha 2025的轶事＃8</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514981</link><description>- 女朋友，你明白这一点。童贞的恢复非常可怕吗？&lt;br /&gt; - 不。只有前两次或三次。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514981</guid></item><item><title>25 Martha 2025的轶事＃9</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514982</link><description>-  Rzhevsky中尉！您有一件新的制服和一把新手表，您从哪里得到这么多钱？&lt;br /&gt; - 我女友的丈夫提高了薪水。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514982</guid></item><item><title>25 Martha 2025的轶事＃10</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514983</link><description>- 达金，您今天想在床上尝试什么？&lt;br /&gt; -Citramon。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-25/#1514983</guid></item></channel></rss>